Package: houghPrimitives
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive 3D Shape Detection for LiDAR Point Clouds
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-03-12
Authors@R: c(
    person("Andrew", "Sánchez Meador", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "andrew.sanchezmeador@nau.edu")
    )
Description: Implements Iterative Hough Transform methods for detecting
    geometric primitives in 3D point clouds. Supports detection of lines,
    planes, spheres, cylinders (tree boles), and cuboids (buildings).
    Fully compatible with lidR package for LiDAR data processing.
    Designed for forestry and urban LiDAR applications.
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.8.3)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
